The Nigeria Customs Service (NCS) Public Relations Officer, Mr. Joseph Attah, has confirmed the death of ex- Comptroller General, Abdullahi Dikko. In a statement, the PRO said: “The family of the former Comptroller General of Customs, Abdullahi Dikko Inde just announced his passing away today. “His funeral prayers (Janaza ) will take  place tomorrow, Friday 19th February, 2020 after Jumaat Prayers at National Mosque Abuja. “He was the Comptroller General of Customs from 2009 to 2015. “May Allah Forgive his shortcomings and may Aljannatul Firdausi be his final abode. “May Allah give his family and loved ones the fortitude to bear the irreparable loss. Amin”.